@amitsela @bjchambers @staslev 

I went ahead and split the PR into 2 commits, one for the metrics support, the other for exposing the metrics via Spark's metrics sink.

I also took care of several of the issues you've raised in comments.

@bjchambers PTAL especially at the changes made in the SDK test classes: `MetricsTest` and `MetricsMatcher` as I've leveraged this RunnableOnService test for testing the implementation in spark, as discussed, and in the course of doing so added to the existing test.
